Melissa Fitzgerald https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Melissa_Fitzgerald 0 Melissa Fitzgerald is an American actress and the Senior Director of the nonprofit organization Justice For Vets. She is best known for portraying Carol Fitzpatrick on The West Wing. Melissa_Fitzgerald is an_American_actress and the_Senior_Director of the_nonprofit_organization_Justice For Vets .
